{"type": "article", "id": 6233, "title": "多功能家具 Woodieful chair", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-15T07:53:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234217orACYf4NpZI9ViS1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t这是一款不愿意安心只做好一款凳子的多功能家具 Woodieful chair。与一般的翻转式多功能家具相比较，这款  Woodieful chair 胜在造型简单利落，可根据使用者的不同需求改变其用途，边桌、杂志架或是小凳子的身份它都能够兼得，而仅杂志的收纳方法就能变化出好几个花样。在设计师 Klavdija Jarc 看来，木材是与家具互动的最佳材质，大家在居家生活环境中接触最多的就是家具，而木头显然比其他材质更能温暖人心。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234214jc79GC6lYKTBOrEx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234215e72khnHp3TP5WF4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234215XmjBQU84YaO75ShG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234216BOtpm7vc3MsjlfLJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234216ckoemOfHUGuStWID.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}